Justine Toms about her book,

00:10:48.860 --> 00:10:49.670 align:middle line:10%
"True Work--

00:10:49.670 --> 00:10:53.092 align:middle line:10%
The Sacred Dimension of Earning
a Living," that she co-authored

00:10:53.092 --> 00:10:55.517 align:middle line:10%
with her husband, Michael Toms.

